[25:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'skill. Now, let\'s talk about the most powerful skill available to you inside of Claude Code, and that is the skill creator skill, which is our next concept. The skill creator skill is not only good because it is trained to create high-quality skills, but it'

[25:44] [scene:talk]
