[26:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'all? And it allows us to test skill improvements. So, if you edit a skill, it will test it against the original iteration. And when I say test it, it runs multiple tests and gives us back actual quantifiable data. This is'

[26:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'massive. In order to use the skill creator skill, just like the front end design skill, you can either copy this URL and bring it to Claude Code, or you can head to the plugin marketplace, find the skill creator skill here, install it, reload your plugins, and you\'re all'

[26:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'ready to go. Now, let\'s talk about some external tools we can bring into Claude Code with concept number 20 and 21, and that is MCPs and CLI tools. So, MCPs are a way for us to connect Claude Code to'

