[27:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'between us and these programs like Notion, I can then just talk to Claude Code in natural language and say, "Hey, do X, Y, and Z inside of Notion." And it will do it for us on our behalf just'

[27:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'like as if we were inside of Notion executing those tasks manually. So, to use these MCP tools requires a couple things. One, you need the specific command. Like I said, the most popular ones can be found here inside of the'

