VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Claude Code documentation, which you can find by either searching Claude Code docs MCP or just asking Claude Code to do it. And then you\'re just going to copy this command, and then you\'re going to paste it inside the terminal. Now,'

[28:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the easier way to actually do this is to just say something like, "Set up the MCP server for Notion for me." Claude Code will do all this on your'

[28:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
